 in the \"contrarians\" subpopulation $\\cal B$ for strong and\nweak cross-population coupling, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Feb 2021 18:12:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-14"}
