usion. Conclusion:\nTask assignment that promotes highly connected team communication networks may\nmitigate tacit knowledge loss in global software teams. Additionally, while\nmembers expressing openness to experience are likely to be particularly driven\nto perform, this is not entirely responsible for a global team's success.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Feb 2021 21:20:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-26"}
